{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji27.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给沈雁冰的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给沈雁冰的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年9月23日）雁冰兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"示悉。写了一句话，作为题词，未知可用否？封面宜由兄写，或请沫若?兄写，不宜要我写。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月二十三日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]沈雁冰，当时任中华全国文学艺术工作者协会副主席、《人民文学》主编。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]指毛泽东1949年9月23日给《人民文学》创刊号写的题词“希望有更多好作品出世”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[3]沫若，即郭沫若。当时任中华全国文学艺术工作者协会主席。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":23}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":298,"page_end":298},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}